147
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:34,160
During my postgrad exam period,

148
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,160
as a supporter of equal rights

149
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:38,120
and women's empowerment,

150
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:41,600
I needed to earn my advisor's favor

151
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:44,000
while maintaining good grades.

152
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,160
Because my graduate advisor

153
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,880
is a woman.

154
00:05:48,307 --> 00:05:49,120
(Student Union Office)

155
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,160
Thanks for your honesty.

156
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,400
I think highly of you.

157
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:55,440
Your spirit mirrors my past self.

158
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,120
Keep it up.

159
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,560
You can go now.

160
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:20,440
Hang the 'closed' sign on the door.

161
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,320
I want to be alone now.

162
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:55,800
We're closed.

163
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,080
Closed.

164
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,520
You still can't forgive me.

165
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:11,960
The gallery is beautiful.

166
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,800
The story is great too.

167
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,080
But this is not what I want.

168
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,120
What do you want?

169
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:20,080
What can I give you? What else can I do?

170
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,120
I want my mom.

171
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,960
I wanted your protection for her then.

172
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,720
I wanted a beautiful childhood.

173
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:39,720
I'm sorry, I'm so sorry.

174
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,520
Through these years,

175
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:49,720
I always want to find a good opportunity

176
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:53,240
to say I'm sorry to you.

177
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,320
I am your father.

178
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,240
But I am unworthy.

179
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,720
I didn't take good care of your mother.

180
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,720
Nor did I take good care of you.

181
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:11,400
I don't expect you
to call me 'dad' again.

182
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,520
But,

183
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,520
I just want to make amends

184
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:20,160
for all my mistakes over the years.

185
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:24,840
Now,

186
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:29,600
I often dream of
the moment you were born.

187
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:31,800
I think that period

188
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:34,400
was the happiest time of my life.

189
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,160
After your mother died,

190
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:44,520
I have lost interest in everything.

191
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:46,360
It's true.

192
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,520
I once enjoyed earning money.

193
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:53,960
Because I needed to
take good care of your mom

194
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,040
and you.

195
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:57,080
But,

196
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,840
since your mom passed away,

197
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:03,200
my life has completely lost direction.

198
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,040
I love your mom deeply.

199
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:07,200
I love you deeply too.

200
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,720
But every time I look into your eyes,

201
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,520
my heart aches terribly.

202
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,360
I can't even

203
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,520
forgive myself.

204
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:26,520
How can I hope

205
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,080
that you can call me "dad" again?

206
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:33,160
I've thought about leaving this city,

207
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,760
far behind,

208
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:38,360
disappearing completely from your life.

209
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,400
But when I see your paintings,

210
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:44,840
which reminds me of your mother,

211
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:49,520
I realize I can't leave you.

212
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,960
I can never leave you.

213
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:01,600
I think you've finished. Here's the key.

214
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:11,200
Thank you for everything these years.

215
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,080
Dad.

216
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:48,520
School is about to start.

217
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,280
The first week,

218
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,760
is the Film Festival presentation.

219
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:55,640
Where is your work?

220
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:58,600
Speak up!

221
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:00,520
Gone mute?

222
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:05,200
I've already sent it to you.

223
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,760
Yes, you did.

224
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,640
Didn't you see what you sent me?

225
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,080
A pile of garbage.

226
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:13,760
Worse than garbage.

227
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:14,920
You call that a film?

228
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:16,040
You're insulting film!

229
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,600
I'm the organizer of such a grand

230
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,760
Film Festival.

231
00:11:20,920 --> 00:11:23,160
But you disgrace me with these trashes.

232
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:25,160
How did you swear to me

233
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:25,760
and promise me?

234
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,040
You said, "We'll do it well."

235
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:31,280
We'll bring honor to our school.

236
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:33,160
And now?

237
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:34,920
Liars!

238
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:37,960
Someone even sent me a 90-second clip.

239
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:41,080
Now, even TikToks are longer than that!

240
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,960
I've told you to work hard in holiday.

241
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:46,040
Then I'll help you to win the award.

242
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:47,760
The prize money will all belongs to you.

243
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:48,640
But what did you do?

244
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,600
Some couldn't be contacted.

245
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:52,360
Some went travelling.

246
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:54,040
There's even some said

247
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:57,040
their hands cramped from playing games

248
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:58,360
and couldn't carry the camera.

249
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:01,760
What lousy excuses these are!

250
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,360
I'm talking about you.

251
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,480
Still playing, huh?

252
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:14,480
I know.

253
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,920
