256
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,480
If you make a good film,

257
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,520
isn't it an honor you receive at school?

258
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:26,640
Didn't you let us participate

259
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:28,720
