262
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,200
What do you mean?

263
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,640
When did I kick her off?

264
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:39,840
She left
because she couldn't handle the task.

265
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:42,200
I aim to expand the Film Festival,

266
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:44,600
to lead you win awards in the city.

267
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:45,760
So you just work hard.

268
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,840
The jury is arranged by me.

269
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,600
All of you will be able to win an award.

270
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,920
I'd be honored too.

271
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,400
Understand?

272
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:54,920
What are you waiting for?

273
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:56,040
Now get to work!

274
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:05,520
Zheng Nan and Liu Yang, you stay.

275
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,360
What I just said,

276
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,360
don't take it seriously.

277
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:16,080
I was addressing the group.

278
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:19,040
What you two filmed is not long enough.

279
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,360
The content is too dull.

280
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:22,480
But the idea is good.

281
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:26,400
Keep working in this direction.

282
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:27,920
Understand?

283
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:32,040
I'm sure you'll win the first prize.

284
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:34,960
This way, the first

285
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,760
